日志与System.out的区别









默认级别是INFO，在INFO级别之下的比如DEBUG就不能输出出来

查看日志级别 Ctrl + Shift + T

搜索类名Level (org.slf4j.event) 


<dependency>
   <groupId>org.projectlombok</groupId>
   <artifactId>lombok</artifactId>
</dependency>
需要配合 Lombok 插件使用 
@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)
@SpringBootTest
@Slf4j
public class LoggerTest {
    
    @Test
    public void test1() {
        log.debug("debug...");
        log.info("info...");
        log.error("error...");
    }
}

2018-08-06 14:48:20.550 ERROR 31812 --- [           main] com.imooc.sell.LoggerTest                : error... 
@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)
@SpringBootTest
@Slf4j
public class LoggerTest {

    @Test
    public void test1() {
        String name = "imooc";
        String password = "123456";
        log.debug("debug...");
        log.info("name: " + name + ", password: " + password);
        log.info("name: {}, password: {}", name, password);
        log.error("error...");
    }
}
2018-08-06 14:46:04.743  INFO 17604 --- [           main] com.imooc.sell.LoggerTest                : name: imooc, password: 123456
2018-08-06 14:46:04.743  INFO 17604 --- [           main] com.imooc.sell.LoggerTest                : name: imooc, password: 123456
2018-08-06 14:46:04.743 ERROR 17604 --- [           main] com.imooc.sell.LoggerTest                : error...


application.yml 只能配置简单的配置：日志文件路径，日志文件输出格式等等

logback-spring.xml 能够配置复杂配置。比如以下需求：


Application.yml格式 

logging:
  pattern:
    console: "%d - %msg%n"

2018-08-06 14:59:07,726 - error...

  pattern:

  # 指定包\类日志级别
  level:

logback-spring.xml格式 
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>

<configuration>

    <appender name="consoleLog" class="ch.qos.logback.core.ConsoleAppender">
        <layout class="ch.qos.logback.classic.PatternLayout">
            <pattern>
                %d - %msg%n
            </pattern>
        </layout>
    </appender>

    <root level="info">
        <appender-ref ref="consoleLog" />
    </root>

</configuration>
2018-08-06 16:52:56,154 - name: imooc, password: 123456
2018-08-06 16:52:56,154 - name: imooc, password: 123456
2018-08-06 16:52:56,154 - error... 
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>

<configuration>

    <!--控制台打印格式-->
    <appender name="consoleLog" class="ch.qos.logback.core.ConsoleAppender">
        <layout class="ch.qos.logback.classic.PatternLayout">
            <pattern>
                %d - %msg%n
            </pattern>
        </layout>
    </appender>

    <!--每天输出一个INFO日志文件-->
    <appender name="fileInfoLog" class="ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.RollingFileAppender">
        <!--拦截等级-->
        <filter class="ch.qos.logback.classic.filter.LevelFilter">
            <level>ERROR</level>
            <onMatch>DENY</onMatch>
            <onMismatch>ACCEPT</onMismatch>
        </filter>
        <encoder>
            <pattern>
                %msg%n
            </pattern>
        </encoder>
        <!--滚动策略-->
        <rollingPolicy class="ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.TimeBasedRollingPolicy">
            <!--路径-->
            <fileNamePattern>D:\developer_tools\apache-tomcat-7.0.78\logs\sell\info.%d.log</fileNamePattern>
        </rollingPolicy>
    </appender>

    <!--每天输出一个ERROR日志文件-->
    <appender name="fileErrorLog" class="ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.RollingFileAppender">
        <!--最低门槛-->
        <filter class="ch.qos.logback.classic.filter.ThresholdFilter">
            <level>ERROR</level>
        </filter>
        <encoder>
            <pattern>
                %msg%n
            </pattern>
        </encoder>
        <!--滚动策略-->
        <rollingPolicy class="ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.TimeBasedRollingPolicy">
            <!--路径-->
            <fileNamePattern>D:\developer_tools\apache-tomcat-7.0.78\logs\sell\error.%d.log</fileNamePattern>
        </rollingPolicy>
    </appender>

    <root level="info">
        <appender-ref ref="consoleLog" />
        <appender-ref ref="fileInfoLog" />
        <appender-ref ref="fileErrorLog" />
    </root>

</configuration>
